{"tid":1965722,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[莫縮叔台] FINAL FANTASY VII REMAKE (PS4)","createTime":"2020-04-09T15:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T16:24:57.000Z","uid":84983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3e3a346c16173105527657a547c327984d7c7409","tid":1965722,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:59:55.000Z","msg":"[莫縮叔台] FINAL FANTASY VII REMAKE (PS4)<br />\n<br />\n莫縮叔遊戲台<br />\n每個星期五、六、日晚上，<br />\n跟大家一邊傾計，一邊打機<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twitch.tv/mokuncle/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fmokuncle%2F&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=d43cc849\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twitch.tv/mokuncle/</a><br />\n<br />\n「跨越世紀、等待了二十餘載的首度中文化經典重生之作！」<br />\n《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》是史克威爾艾尼克斯預定於2020年4月10日在全球推出的遊戲軟體。將在PlayStation 4平台先行推出，獨占時間為1年。該遊戲為1997年在PS平台推出的Final Fantasy系列第七作《Final Fantasy VII》的完全重製作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1585/15855271/3652347-3532489-final%20fantasy%207%20remake.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamespot1.cbsistatic.com%2Fuploads%2Foriginal%2F1585%2F15855271%2F3652347-3532489-final%2520fantasy%25207%2520remake.jpg&h=b806c584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n========================<br />\n莫縮叔Facebook Page <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/MokUncle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMokUncle&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=99c1b6ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/MokUncle</a>"},{"pid":"9f437b6cec7b278f5baa5b3ddb7d31f01a51f106","tid":1965722,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T16:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e910db6f78e6d1ce1f2204344cf245945433f4","tid":1965722,"uid":84983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0